						<summary>

						<p>East wall of the same temple, right of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Parakēsarivarman</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Tribhº Vikrama-chōḷadēva: Year 12 = 1284-85 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of a garden as <hi rend="italic">maḍappuṟam</hi> made by the residents of Śōḻamādēvinallūr in Karaivaḻi-nāḍu, to the <hi rend="italic">Kīḻaimaṭham</hi> (the monastery on the eastern side) for burning lamps in the <hi rend="italic">maṭham.</hi></p>						

