<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> kopparakecaripaṉmarāṉa tiripuvaṉacakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vikkiramacoḻatevaṟku tiruveḻu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ttiṭṭu cellāniṉṟa tiru<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>elliyāṇṭu <num value="12"><g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num> vatu karaivaḻināṭṭu coḻamātevinallūr Ūr 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rom Eṅkaḷḷūr kiḻaimaṭattil mutaliyār <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> lla ñānām pata(ta)kku nāṅkaḷ I<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied>maṭattukku maṭappuṟamā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ka tiruviḷakkiṭaviṭṭa toṭṭattukku nāṉkellaiyāvatu kiḻpākkellai vaṭakku nokkipoṉa kar<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kku meṟkum teṉpākkellai nāṅkaḷ Ellai nāṭṭiṉakallukku vaṭakkum melpākkellai Iṭṭalu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kku kiḻakkum vaṭapākkellai nāṅkaḷ Ellai nāṭṭiṉakallukku teṟkum Iṉnāṉ kellaikuḷuḷ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḷiṭṭa toṭṭam maṭa<supplied reason="omitted">p</supplied>puṟamāka viṭṭukkuṭuttom coḻamātevinallūrvarom Imaṭappuṟam caṉtirā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tittavaṟ celvatāka kalveṭṭikkuṭuttom coḻamātevinallūr Ūrom Ippaṭikku
</p>

